    "syllabus": "統計計算課程介紹如何利用統計計算與模擬的基本方法及技巧來進行統計分析。講解如何藉由電腦軟體產生隨機變數，了解抽樣分配及利用電腦軟體進行統計分析的步驟及應用。\n\n*   Introduction to Statistical Computing and R\n    \n*   Review of Probability and Sampling distribution \n    \n*   Simple Random Sampling with R\n    \n*   Statistical Inference: Estimation and Simulation:\n    \n*   Bootstrap Methodology with R \n    \n*   Linear Regression Analysis with R\n    \n*   Variable Selection using LASSO Regression\n    \n*   Mixture Model",
